                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
                        alſo ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l6">mẅen vnd ʒu <expan>tege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> / mag eẅr gnade wol
