                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l9">Jch laſſ mıch <expan>bedunke<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ
                        ſıch <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel vnd der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> meinr <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_422_r1l10"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> . ſouil noch niht
